What news?

585
00:44:05,690 --> 00:44:07,650
Anything you want to tell me?

586
00:44:10,050 --> 00:44:11,290
No.

587
00:44:13,850 --> 00:44:15,610
OK. Well... look...

588
00:44:15,610 --> 00:44:17,570
I'll call you tomorrow?

