613
00:48:57,090 --> 00:48:58,450
You're back.

614
00:49:33,730 --> 00:49:37,170
Hey! I saw your car. You said two days.

615
00:49:37,170 --> 00:49:40,450
I changed my mind. I
didn't want to be away.

616
00:49:43,850 --> 00:49:46,650
I'm all over the place at
